Q. Do all shoppers have to necessarily register before checking out the orders?
<br>
A. Not required. One can place an order without any registration.

<br><br>
Q. How to register on the website?
<br>
A. Click on "Log In" on the right hand corner. Click on "Create a new account".Registration can also be done at the time of checking out the order.

<br><br>
Q. Which areas are you serving?
<br>
A. We are currently providing the service to residents of a few select apartment complexes in Bangalore near Hoody circle. Such residents can readily register on the website and enjoy our services.     Other residents, who are interested in our services, can please email us at admin@attachawal.com mentioning their address. We will come back to you once we start providing our delivery services to their residential areas.
<br><br>

Q. What are the various payment methods available?
<br>
A. We will accept cash at the time of delivery.

<br><br>

Q. When will you deliver my order?
<br>
A. Orders will be delivered twice a week, i.e, Sunday morning 9-11 am and Thursday 8-10 pm. You can choose any one day for delivery. But if you want your order to be delivered on Sunday then the order should be raised before 5pm on Saturday. Similarly, for Thursday, order should be raised on Wednesday before 5 pm.

<br><br>

Q. Can I cancel an order?
<br>
A. Yes you can cancel your order over the phone before the order cut-off time. For Sunday delivery, it is Saturday 5 pm  and for Thursday it is Wednesday 5 pm. Call 9986698343

<br><br>
Q. Can I amend / update my order after placing it
<br>
A. No, But you can raise another order. Both orders will be delivered

<br><br>

Q. What is the return and refund policy at attachawal?
<br>
A. If the product is damaged then it will be exchanged.

<br><br>
Q. Will I get any discounts for my orders?
<br>
A. Yes, all the products will be below mrp. For special discount you can click on the "Offers" appear on right side of the page.

<br><br>


Q. Is there is any least amount for which I have to place an order?
<br>
A. No there is no limit. You can order only one maggi also.
<br><br>

